skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cabin fever
des:
Ask Cabin Fever for free things to do while you are holed up.

Cabin Fever recommends fun and interesting things you can enjoy from home. From virtual tours, concerts, and things to learn; to quick challenges and things to make.

To start, just say "Alexa, ask Cabin Fever for something to do." or "Alexa, open Cabin fever to get an idea".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
